title: NCAAFB, stars leaving, top WRs, Ezekiel Elliott
itunes:title: NCAAFB, stars leaving, top WRs, Ezekiel Elliott
description:
Colin discusses college football cutting needless games, J.J. Redick's comments on why there is so much backlash when stars leave teams, the top 10 WRs in the NFL, and his thoughts on an anonymous offensive coach saying Ezekiel Elliott isn't a top 10 RB. Guests include Chris Broussard, Joel Klatt, Will Blackmon, and Jason McIntyre.
